name: Zohan
description:
Tired of all the struggles in his country, a legendary Israeli military named Zohan fakes his own death and moves to New York, where he can fulfill his big dream: to become a famous hairdresser.
Release Date: June 6, 2008 (USA)
Director: Dennis Dugan
Music composed by: Rupert Gregson-Williams
Screenplay: Adam Sandler; Robert Smigel; Judd Apatow
In Brazil: Zohan: A Good Cutting Agent
Budget: US$90 million
